
<div class="comments-form p-lg-5 mt-4">
    <h3>Yorum Bırak </h3>
    <p>E-posta adresiniz yayınlanmayacak. Gerekli alanlar * ile işaretlenmiştir.</p>
    <form  method="post" class="comment_form">
        <div class="row form-row">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <input type="hidden" placeholder="id" name="IlanId" value=" @ViewBag.deger" required />
                <div class="form-group">
                    <textarea name="Yorum" id="msgt" cols="30" rows="6" placeholder="Yorumunuz.." class="form-control"></textarea>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="İsminiz" name="KullaniciAdi">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="form-group" >
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Mail Adresiniz" name="Mail">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="form-group" >
                    <input type="submit" class="btn btn-main" value="Gönder" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </form>
</div>

